title: can't create labeled videos
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Bug description

hey,
I'm trying to create some labeled videos after DLC finished training without problems.
I'm using the GUI so i just followed the steps as written in the paper.
there are several warnings that pop when i finish analyzing new videos and again when i try to create the labeled video.
so first in the analyze step : Failed to launch ptxas, that's related to TF but until now everything worked ok so that's weird
and then it seems to be the problem to the rest of the process. DLC can't find filtered/unfiltered data file even though h5 files created.
I copied the terminal message for your convenience, as you can see i'm not a programmer so it will be nice to keep the explanation in simple terms if possible. also i tried to resolve this issue by other questions asked here and without success. 
thank you very much!

### Operating System

windows 10

### DeepLabCut version

2.2.0.3

### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type

gpu RTX 2080 Ti

### Steps To Reproduce

_No response_
